reviews.text: Bad hygiene. There are at least two flies in my spaghetti soup.
Another local BBQ joint which was so tasty and great price.
bad food and bad service.

Tried a bit of everything roasted. Overall passable. Char Siew is probably the best here. Roast duck was a tad salty. Thought I ordered 烧肉but what came was more like suckling pig. OK, but skin was not crispy as it could have been. Soya sauce chicken was smooth and not bad but some might say bone was a bit bloody. To me it was ok.
It is just ok

reviews.text: 好👌
位於北角道11-13號4號舖的太平燒味飯店，化皮乳猪和燒肉都唔錯，這裡早餐也多元化，價錢也公道，但地方细小！
這間店舖坐位太窄食物質素尚可以至於凍奶茶調校味道淡咗有待改進
服務一般，食品值得光顧
烧肉叉烧硬，难咀嚼和吞咽。切鸡有血水，虽然较滑，但不敢吃。味道中下。
